Flyout, SettingsContractWrapper, HeaderedTextBox, HeaderedTextBlock, LabeledProgressBar, LineCounter, RandomColorGenerator, LayoutAwarePage, SilentTextBox, KeyboardDismissingComboBox and extension methods for localizing enums

Windows Phone:
